Class ValueTooHighException

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ValueTooHighException
extends InvalidValueException

    Indicates that a given value was too high for a given Variable.

    The error code will always be ERROR_CODE_INCLUSIVE or ERROR_CODE_EXCLUSIVE.
